00:19:31.280 Let me ask you a practical question. If
00:19:33.720 every microservice was a separate Java
00:19:35.560 project,
00:19:37.080 imagine the problem.
00:19:38.560 If you have 14 microservices,
00:19:41.280 you would have to open 14
00:19:43.640 different IntelliJ projects.
00:19:46.480 If you change one shared class, you
00:19:48.960 would need to update it in every
00:19:51.360 project.
00:19:52.800 And managing version would become messy.
00:19:56.560 One service might use Spring Boot 4.0.1,
00:20:01.280 another 4.0.2.
00:20:04.120 That quickly become hard to manage. So,
00:20:06.720 what do we do?
00:20:10.720 We use Maven multi-module.
00:20:13.880 With Maven multi-module, we keep
00:20:16.000 everything inside one main project.
00:20:19.960 All service live inside it. One build
00:20:22.520 command builds everything.
00:20:25.800 Everything stays organized, consistent,
00:20:28.800 and easy to manage.
00:20:31.960 Now,
00:20:33.000 let's understand
00:20:35.160 what a Maven multi-module project
00:20:37.320 actually is.
00:20:40.160 A Maven multi-module project is
00:20:42.320 basically one big project that contains
00:20:45.800 multiple smaller projects inside it.
00:20:49.680 Think of it like a main project with
00:20:52.200 many sub projects, like user service,
00:20:54.720 booking service, airline service,
00:20:56.800 payment service, etc.
00:20:59.560 In Maven term,
00:21:01.800 the main project is called
00:21:04.760 parent.
00:21:06.880 The parent project knows
00:21:09.920 about all the modules
00:21:12.800 and the modules inherit configuration
00:21:16.520 from the parent.
00:21:18.400 So, instead of configuring things again
00:21:21.280 and again in every services, we define
00:21:24.800 them once in parent.
00:21:28.480 Now, the best part
00:21:30.720 is how simple the workflow becomes.
00:21:36.160 One Git repository, single repository,
00:21:39.400 one IntelliJ project, and one build
00:21:43.040 command.
00:21:44.720 Maven clean install builds everything.
00:21:50.960 That means you don't need to build every
00:21:53.800 service manually.
00:21:55.960 Just run one Maven command and Maven
00:21:59.200 will build all modules automatically.
00:22:02.560 That's the power of Maven multi-module
00:22:05.040 project.
00:22:07.640 Now, let's understand why multi-module.
00:22:14.880 Imagine you are starting a tiny airline
00:22:18.160 called Joes Airline.
00:22:20.680 At the beginning, it's just you.
00:22:23.240 You sell the ticket, you clean the
